{"about_the_game":"The Mines of Frostheim is a classic dungeon crawler jrpg.  Set in a mining town, high atop a dark mountain, with a monster-infested mine full of treasure and jewels at its feet, you must help the Guilds explore the depths and unlock the secret to help restore the mine back to its former glory and rid it of the monsters within.<br><br>This game features a wide variety of unique attributes such as:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic Dungeon Crawler experience.<br></li><li>Character Customization.  Recruit up to 10 characters you create and name.<br></li><li>Randomly Generated Floors to allow for better re-playablility.<br></li><li>No random encounters.  All monsters are visible and can be stealthily avoided.<br></li><li>An Active Time Battle system, allowing for fast-paced action, minimizing time spent in battle.<br></li><li>Randomized Loot system, featuring multiple tiers of affixes on different item rarities.<br>  -50+ Unique Affixes<br>  -10 Tiers levels for each affix<br>  -5 Rarity types for equipment<br>  -500+ Different weapons and armours to find<br>  -Hundreds of thousands of combinations for equipment!<br></li><li>9 different classes to choose from, each with their own skills/magic.<br></li><li>Item customization systems with cores and Gem types.<br></li><li>Item bank and storage system.<br></li><li>Main Story Quest.<br></li><li>Repeatable Guild Quests system.<br></li><li>60 Steam Achievements to get.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1770810/8f315e90fd2d7732018d31b3522e06d98ae34ed1.jpg"},{"name":"Fighter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1770810/f6430c86dd737a0a7a53ed03e43496b397717237.jpg"},{"name":"Warrior","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1770810/0f494205787aec75d4b1208b73ca8ecc2587c120.jpg"},{"name":"Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steam